\": \"And Utahns can watch the announcement live at a party outside the Salt Lake City and County Building.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999991077857, \"rank\": 7.941763975603326e-10, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Utahns\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"the announcement\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 221}, {\"ngram\": \"a party\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Park City will gather to celebrate later Wednesday.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\", \"score\": 0.9999964802946675, \"rank\": 3.519717824248765e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Utah Olympic Park will host festivities including live music, vendors, giveaways, pin trading and an Olympic and Paralympian meet and greet.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 344, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.924599494459878e-16, \"text\": \"Utah Olympic Park\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"festivities\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"live music\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"vendors\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"giveaways\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"pin trading\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"greet\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event runs from 4 p.m. to 9 p.m.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The event\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"4 p.m.\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"9 p.m.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Flying Ace All-Stars Freestyle show is free at 6:30 p.m., but tickets are sold out.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Flying Ace All-Stars Freestyle show\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"6:30 p.m.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Park City Economic Development Program Manager Jenny Diersen said no parking is available on site.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\", \"score\": 0.9999964802946675, \"rank\": 3.519717824248765e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City_Mountain_Resort\"}, {\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Program_Manager\", \"score\": 0.9633389168242115, \"rank\": 0.038056267151133485, \"text\": \"Program Manager\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Program_Manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Program_Manager\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Lake\", \"score\": 0.9999032356084961, \"rank\": 9.6666413108671